I understand.
I understand.

35:00.900 --> 35:02.560
[SORROWFUL MUSIC]

35:02.560 --> 35:04.190
JIM: Lydia.

35:06.030 --> 35:07.460
[LYDIA GASPS]

35:07.460 --> 35:09.030
JIM: I'd love to see you again.

35:09.030 --> 35:11.060
Yes. I'll see you at school.

35:13.400 --> 35:15.430
JIM: Good night.

35:22.680 --> 35:24.690
[CRYING]

36:11.190 --> 36:13.200
[GLASS SHATTERING]

36:25.310 --> 36:29.190
She's unable to maintain
a steady job.

36:29.190 --> 36:31.650
