to school without breakfast,

36:31.650 --> 36:34.980
let alone lunch.
I've often seen him

36:34.980 --> 36:38.010
unwashed, wearing dirty clothes.

36:39.490 --> 36:41.720
AGENT: Do they go to church?

36:41.720 --> 36:42.900
LYDIA: I've tried.

36:44.040 --> 36:46.110
She carries on with men.

36:46.110 --> 36:48.470
I know of three
in the last few months.

36:48.470 --> 36:49.890
One of whom was married.

36:49.890 --> 36:51.400
[AGENT GRUNTS IN DISGUST]

36:52.450 --> 36:53.880
Is there really enough here

36:53.880 --> 36:55.570
to trigger an emergency removal?

36:59.140 --> 37:02.250
The child is vulnerable

37:02.250 --> 37:04.780
to a corrupting influence.

37:04.780 --> 37:07.320
We are required by law

37:07.320 --> 37:09.320
to report moral weakness,

37:09.320 --> 37:11.160
Mr. Thorne.

37:14.450 --> 37:16.890
AGENT: In my judgment,
Miss Clements' assessment

37:16.890 --> 37:18.260
of this case is accurate,

37:18.260 --> 37:20.250
and the correct steps
have been taken.

37:20.250 --> 37:21.460
Okay.

37:21.460 --> 37:22.570
AGENT: If you just could sign
at the bottom, please.

37:22.570 --> 37:25.000
Mmm-hmm.

37:25.000 --> 37:26.030
Here?

37:26.030 --> 37:29.440
AGENT: Yes.
Don't worry about Ryan.

37:29.440 --> 37:30.860
He's in a proper
foster home now,

37:30.860 --> 37:32.250
I can assure you. Hmm.

37:32.250 --> 37:33.650
AGENT: And there's a long list

37:33.650 --> 37:35.850
of wonderful couples
who are desperate to adopt.

37:35.850 --> 37:38.280
I'm sure.

37:38.280 --> 37:41.480
So many people...

37:41.480 --> 37:44.090
with so much...

37:44.090 --> 37:46.040
love to give.

37:48.030 --> 37:49.060
Thank you.

37:49.060 --> 37:50.460
NOELLE: Get off me!

37:50.460 --> 37:52.030
Where is she?
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

37:52.030 --> 37:54.650
SECURITY: Ma'am!

37:54.650 --> 37:55.980
Ma'am!
[NOELLE CRYING]

37:57.240 --> 37:59.030
NOELLE: How could you do this to us?

37:59.030 --> 38:00.200
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

38:00.200 --> 38:01.460
I had to,

38:01.460 --> 38:02.740
to protect Ryan.

38:02.740 --> 38:03.780
From what?

38:03.780 --> 38:04.820
[STUTTERING]
He's fine!

38:04.820 --> 38:05.850
He needs me!

38:05.850 --> 38:07.540
- He needs his mother!
- AGENT: Ma'am,

38:07.540 --> 38:09.740
you're entitled to appeal our
determination at your hearing

38:09.740 --> 38:11.680
in six weeks.
Six weeks!

38:11.680 --> 38:12.930
Why?

38:12.930 --> 38:14.370
This is your fault, Noelle.

38:14.370 --> 38:15.920
You must know that.

38:15.920 --> 38:17.320
You're ruining his life.

38:17.320 --> 38:19.060
You're a fucking coldhearted bitch!

38:19.060 --> 38:20.450
SECURITY: Ma'am! Ma'am.
NOELLE: That's never... She doesn't...

38:20.450 --> 38:21.480
I forgive you.

38:21.480 --> 38:22.480
NOELLE: No! This isn't right...

38:22.480 --> 38:23.510
SECURITY: Calm down!

38:23.510 --> 38:26.030
NOELLE: This is her fault!
This is...

38:26.030 --> 38:27.650
You are ruining his life,

38:27.650 --> 38:30.450
you fucking bitch!
It's her!

38:30.450 --> 38:32.700
SECURITY: Take a breath!
NOELLE: She did this!

38:32.700 --> 38:34.710
[NOELLE SOBBING]

38:54.560 --> 38:55.730
[SIGHS]

39:06.650 --> 39:08.650
We never had issues with Ofjoseph

39:08.650 --> 39:10.040
before the Waterfords.

39:10.040 --> 39:11.260
[LAUGHS BITTERLY]

39:11.260 --> 39:12.480
A problem household,

39:12.480 --> 39:14.110
to say the least.

39:14.110 --> 39:15.740
And she was there
for all that business

39:15.740 --> 39:17.050
with Emily.
Mmm.

39:17.050 --> 39:18.660
AUNT ELIZABETH: And Lillie.

39:18.660 --> 39:20.670
Trouble with two
walking partners.

39:20.670 --> 39:22.050
Now three.

39:22.050 --> 39:24.450
And Ofmatthew is pregnant.

39:24.450 --> 39:26.590
The Calhouns' baby
must be protected.

39:26.590 --> 39:28.170
Not every household

39:28.170 --> 39:30.030
and Handmaid is a good fit.

39:30.030 --> 39:32.960
Environment cannot
be underestimated

39:32.960 --> 39:35.300
as an influence.

39:35.300 --> 39:37.570
Sometimes it's the apple,

39:37.570 --> 39:39.250
and sometimes

39:39.250 --> 39:41.270
it's the barrel.

39:43.230 --> 39:45.240
[WIND HOWLING]

39:45.240 --> 39:48.130
[CURIOUS MUSIC]

40:06.880 --> 40:09.050
OFJOSEPH: <i>I hurt her.</i>

40:09.050 --> 40:11.040
<i>And I enjoyed it.</i>

40:11.040 --> 40:12.940
<i>The Wives and Aunts, too,</i>

40:12.940 --> 40:16.050
<i>grieving over
Ofandy's dead child.</i>

40:16.050 --> 40:17.450
<i>And Lawrence.</i>

40:17.450 --> 40:19.240
<i>They all deserve to suffer.</i>

40:19.240 --> 40:20.250
<i>It's an acquired taste,</i>

40:20.250 --> 40:21.650
<i>seeing others in pain.</i>

40:21.650 --> 40:22.870
<i>Like that smoky scotch</i>

40:22.870 --> 40:24.640
<i>Luke got as a gift once.</i>

40:24.640 --> 40:25.860
<i>I grew to like that.</i>

40:28.230 --> 40:30.500
Blessed be the fruit.

40:30.500 --> 40:32.890
May the Lord open.

40:37.800 --> 40:38.890
[INDISTINCT RADIO CHATTER]

40:38.890 --> 40:40.670
[DOOR BEEPS]

40:40.670 --> 40:42.870
ANNOUNCER: <i>Attention
all Marthas and Handmaids.</i>

40:42.870 --> 40:44.040
<i>Due to the weather,</i>

40:44.040 --> 40:46.260
<i>it is advised to stay
on the main roadways.</i>

40:46.260 --> 40:47.530
<i>Walk with God.</i>

40:48.540 --> 40:51.230
JUNE: <i>I finally
know how Ofglen felt.</i>

40:51.230 --> 40:53.270
<i>What made her
put on that bomb vest.</i>

40:53.270 --> 40:54.660
Hey, hey.

40:54.660 --> 40:56.640
Hey, are you okay?

40:56.640 --> 40:57.750
Yesterday was tough.

40:57.750 --> 40:59.030
I'm fine.

40:59.030 --> 41:00.650
Ofjoseph.

41:00.650 --> 41:02.670
A word, if you please.

41:02.670 --> 41:04.030
[SOFT MUZAK]

41:06.410 --> 41:08.420
Of course, Aunt Lydia.

41:09.460 --> 41:11.750
<i>And I know how Emily felt,</i>

41:11.750 --> 41:14.240
<i>right before she stuck a knife</i>

41:14.240 --> 41:16.440
<i>in Lydia's back.</i>

41:16.440 --> 41:17.870
ANNOUNCER: <i>Attention Handmaids.</i>

41:17.870 --> 41:19.250
<i>Please stay with your partner</i>

41:19.250 --> 41:20.840
<i>at all times.</i>

41:20.840 --> 41:23.210
I was thinking
about you last night.

41:23.210 --> 41:24.870
How I have failed you.

41:24.870 --> 41:26.380
I prayed on it.

41:26.380 --> 41:28.890
Yes, Aunt Lydia?

41:28.890 --> 41:30.690
AUNT LYDIA: All I want is for my girls

41:30.690 --> 41:33.020
