41:40.850 --> 41:41.990
What?

41:41.990 --> 41:43.840
It's become quite clear

41:43.840 --> 41:45.450
that the Lawrence household

41:45.450 --> 41:47.660
is dangerously unorthodox.

41:47.660 --> 41:49.040
First Emily,

41:49.040 --> 41:51.170
then all your recent troubles.

41:51.170 --> 41:52.470
It's my understanding

41:52.470 --> 41:54.950
