requested me personally.

41:54.950 --> 41:56.670
AUNT LYDIA: There are
Commanders more powerful

41:56.670 --> 41:59.100
than Lawrence, dear.

41:59.100 --> 42:00.850
In the end, it's about
the fitness of the family.

42:00.850 --> 42:01.890
It's okay.

42:01.890 --> 42:04.020
AUNT LYDIA: Eleanor is ill, as you know.

42:04.020 --> 42:06.450
And Commander Lawrence...
[OFMATTHEW WHIMPERS]

42:06.450 --> 42:08.180
