Stop it!
Stop it!

42:27.250 --> 42:28.600
Ofmatthew!
[OFMATTHEW GRUNTING]

42:28.600 --> 42:30.630
Stop it!
[JANINE GROANING]

42:30.630 --> 42:32.210
Stop it!
[OFMATTHEW CRYING]

